snippet.title: Adopt Cats at New Animal Shelter ( Sim Game )
snippet.description:
There is a new animal shelter in town that I'm going to work at! This is a new game called Animal Shelter where you can help cats and dogs get adopted and find new homes while taking care of them while they are looking for their new family. 
Have a magical day and I'll see you in my next video! :D
